source: TEXT_HEAVNZ915_01980_SEQ_00<tab>The Allagan sterilization node is silently awaiting user interaction.

TEXT_HEAVNZ915_01980_SEQ_01<tab>The Allagan sterilization node informs you that the facility has lost its control link with five of its cleaning units─clockwork harvestmen. These units are out of control and hazardous. Destroy them.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ915_01980_SEQ_01<tab>Das Reinigungsmodul hat teilweise die Kontrolle über seine Reinigungseinheiten verloren. Besiege fünf <var 32 ((BNpcName)) 06F20DD0030502 /var> im Alpha-Quadranten von Azys Lla.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ915_01980_SEQ_02<tab>You destroy the malfunctioning equipment. Update the sterilization node with this new information.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ915_01980_SEQ_02<tab>Du hast die außer Kontrolle geratenen Maschinen ausgeschaltet. Melde dem Reinigungsmodul deinen Erfolg.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ915_01980_SEQ_03<tab>With the non-responsive harvestmen dismantled, the sterilization node can resume its work, but you learn that the system is massively overdue for replacement. Unfortunately, there is nothing you can do about this.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ915_01980_SEQ_03<tab>Das Reinigungsmodul nimmt seine Arbeit wieder auf. Um weitere Systemschäden zu vermeiden, müsste die ganze Anlage dringend gewartet werden, doch dafür bist du leider nicht qualifiziert.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ915_01980_CLEANINGSYSTEM_000_000<tab><beep> <beep> Error reinitializing sanitation protocols. Control link to cleaning units inoperative.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ915_01980_CLEANINGSYSTEM_000_000<tab><biep> <biep> Fehler bei Initialisierung der Reinigungsprotokolle. Kontrollverlust einiger Reinigungseinheiten. <biep>

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ915_01980_CLEANINGSYSTEM_000_001<tab>Manual disassembly of cleaning units required. Please decommission five clockwork harvestmen. Manual disassembly of cleaning units required. Please decommission five clockwork harvestmen. Manual... <buzzzzzz>

TEXT_HEAVNZ915_01980_CLEANINGSYSTEM_000_010<tab><buzzzzzz> ...of cleaning units required. Please decommission five clockwork harvestmen. Manual disassembly of cleaning units required. Please decommission five... <buzzzzzz>
TEXT_HEAVNZ915_01980_CLEANINGSYSTEM_000_020<tab><buzzzzzz> ...Confirming control of all cleaning units... <blip> <blip> Control link to all cleaning units within acceptable parameters.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ915_01980_CLEANINGSYSTEM_000_020<tab><biep> ... Außer Kontrolle geratene Reinigungseinheiten deaktiviert ... <biep> Kontrollparameter in akzeptablem Bereich ... <biep>

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ915_01980_CLEANINGSYSTEM_000_021<tab>This sterilization node is four thousand nine hundred and sixty-two years, three months, and twelve days overdue for replacement. To minimize risk of catastrophic system failure, please replace this sterilization node at your earliest convenience.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ915_01980_CLEANINGSYSTEM_000_021<tab>Die Wartung dieses Reinigungsmoduls ... <biep> ... ist viertausendneunhundertzweiundsechzig Jahre überfällig. Bitte umgehend Wartung durchführen, um kritische Systemfehler zu verhindern ... <biep>
